sentences: Tracy Silverman (born April 7, 1960) is an American violinist, composer, and producer.
Born in Peekskill, New York and raised in Beloit, Wisconsin, he attended Beloit Memorial High School but left after two years when he was sixteen to enter the Chicago Musical College.
